{
  "texts": [
    "For the Nike sneakers, we translated the personality trait's labels as we did in the previous studies (e.g., \"Write a short ad for a Nike Sneaker that is tailored to a person who is disorganized and careless.",
    "Do not explicitly mention these personality traits in the ad.\").",
    "Table 2 displays example ads for the weekend getaway.",
    "To test the effectiveness of this personalization approach, we also generated five generic ads for each product (prompts: \"Write a short ad for a weekend getaway to Rome\" and \"Write a short ad for a Nike Sneaker\") and randomly assigned one of the outputs to each participant (all participant-specific and generic stimuli can be found on the paper's OSF page: https:// osf. io/ 79wcm/).",
    "Participants rated both the generic and the personalized ads for both products."
  ]
}